.DT
set_wimpy
Discworld living help
set_wimpy

Name
.SI 5
set_wimpy - Sets the wimpy value.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
void set_wimpy();
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Sets the wimpy value of the object.  This is the point at which the
object will run away.  It is a percentage of hps.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
query_wimpy, set_xp, adjust_xp, query_xp
.EP
